OL,5, Courts could grind to a halt without an
OL,6, immediate injection of #135m into the  
OL,7, legal aid system, an independent review
OL,8, has warned.                            
OL,10,FThe report tells ministers to find the 
OL,11,Ffunding to reverse a huge loss of      
OL,12,Flawyers who are vital to the system.   
OL,14,FThe review was launched by ministers   
OL,15,Fthree years ago after predictions the  
OL,16,Flegal aid system could collapse.       
OL,18,FThe Ministry of Justice said it hoped  
OL,19,Fto respond to the report by the end of 
OL,20,FMarch next year.                       
